  "text": "In addition, we borrow the idea from the recent deep residual network [CITATION_1] ] and add one skip-layer to connect fine layers and coarse layers which enable the model to conduct local predictions constrained under the global structure. In our implementation, we adopt ReLU activation layers [CITATION_2] due to its fast convergence rate and a sigmoid activation layer at the end since the residual contains negative value and needs to be clamped.",
